a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball IV

p.k: The Comic / The Romantic / The Uploads Gumball is the star of his own comic, but struggles to match up to his heroic alter-ego. / Gumball tries to recapture the magic with Penny by organising a big romantic gesture. / Gumball and Darwin try to tear themselves away from the internet, but end up falling down the Elmore Stream-hole.
